title useSession Typing (Before)

rectangle "useSession(authClient)" as hook #FCF3CF
rectangle "UseSessionResult\n- data: AthenaAuthSessionResponse | null\n- error: AthenaAuthResult<unknown>['errorDetails']\n- refetch(): Promise<AthenaAuthSessionResponse | null>" as result #F9EBEA

hook --> result

note bottom of result
Return typing is fixed to the default session shape.
Client-specific getSession data narrowing is not propagated.
end note

